title: DnSpy, Hack/Mod your Unity Game Apparently... Good to know.
description: Apparently you can easily read the code of a Unity project and modify it. I learn that on the request of a friend that need a ski game with a real ski training machine. This video is just a reminder of what it looked like to do that in case I need to do it again.
